Sentencas: A cone-shaped gadolinium doped ceria (Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95, GDC) electrolyte cylinder with a thin wall was fabricated using slip casting technique.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The diameter of the larger open end of the cone-shaped cylinder was 0.85 cm, the length was 1.0 cm, and the thickness of the wall was 0.026 cm after sintering.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Both the electrolyte and electrode powders were fabricated by using a glycine-nitrate process.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: A single solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) was prepared with the cone-shaped electrolyte, NiO-GDC (70:30 wt.%) anode and Sm0.5Sr0.5CoO3 (SSC) cathode.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Its electrochemical performance (I-V curve) and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) were studied with humidified hydrogen as the fuel and air as the oxidant.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The maximum output power density was about 300 mW/cm(2) at 700 degrees C.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The EIS results showed that the dominant loss of the SOFC was from the ohmic resistance of the electrolyte.
Titulo: Cone-shaped cylindrical Ce0.9Gd0.1O1.95 electrolyte prepared by slip casting and its application to solid oxide fuel cells
